      <title>夏令营经验</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/zh/blog/experience/master_apply/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/zh/blog/experience/master_apply/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2&gt;TL;DR&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tldr&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tldr&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;




  












